 Description and Requirements 
 
 Lionbridge AI at TELUS International is looking for a Human Resources Manager to join our AI team in US. 
HR manager will oversee all aspects of Human Resources practices and processes. HR Manager will support business needs and ensure the proper implementation of company 
strategy and objectives. 
The goal is to promote corporate values and enable business success through human resources management, including job design, performance management, training and onboarding 
 
RESPONSIBILITIES : 
Acts as HR responsible for TELUS AI employees in Costa Rica, USA and Canada 
Reports to HR Director and works closely with global HR colleagues 
Oversee, refine, and execute employee standards and procedures, using and improving HR existing and recommended systems and processes 
Identify and recommend areas of improvement to internal standard operating procedures 
Champion the onboarding process, ensuring the process is up to date and of high quality, providing clarity and connection for all employees and their role in relation to the overall vision 
Maintain management guidelines by preparing, updating, and recommending local human resource policies and procedures 
Plan, monitor, and appraise HR activities with employees, hearing and resolving employee grievances 
Acts as a labour law expert; monitor, follow-up and study local labour law requirements 
Train managers to coach and discipline employees, and counseling employees and supervisors 
Nurture a positive working environment 
Report to management and provide decision support through HR metrics 
Handle confidential matters with discretion 
SKILLS AND QUALIFICATIONS : 
Bachelorâ€™s degree in human resources 
3+ years in human resources or recruitment 
Experience in working in a multicultural environment, familiarity with working with remote teams 
Excellent English skills, written and spoken. Other language skills is a plus 
Exceptional communication skills, writing skills, interpersonal skills, and ethical mindset 
Adept to problem-solving and conflict resolution 
Extensive knowledge of HR policies and systems 
Familiarity with Workday and working knowledge of GSuite is a plus 
Recognized as an expert in the HR field. 
 
